---
title: Courgette, Broad Bean and Feta Orzotto with Pork Meatballs
description: Anyone say broad beans? Charlotte, our veggie buyer, loves these green British beauties, so begged us to squirrel them into one of the dishes this week. Our chef, Victoria, accepted the challenge and voilà,
a delicious cheesy broad bean orzo. We’re sending you whole broad beans in their jackets (pods), so that they have a little extra safety padding for their journey to your kitchen this evening – happy podding!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/courgette-broad-bean-and-feta-or-5feb0fdf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/courgette-broad-bean-and-feta-or-da69cdb2.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
cuisine: Fusion
